Package de.ipk_gatersleben.ag_nw.graffiti.plugins.gui.webstart

Interface DragAndDropHandler

All Known Subinterfaces:
DataDragAndDropHandler, ExperimentDataDragAndDropHandler
All Known Implementing Classes:
AddonManagerPlugin, TemplateLoader
public interface DragAndDropHandler
Use DataDragAndDropHandler or ExperimentDataDragAndDropHandler in case this handler processes input files for the creation of Substance datasets. If the handler fully processes the input files, implement this interface.

      boolean canProcess​(File f)

    • hasPriority

      boolean hasPriority()
      Returns:
      True, if the handler should be called before other handlers are executed, which return False.
